Operation Transformation - Series 7, Episode 3

Kathryn Thomas checks in on the leaders on their first week, to see if the dramatic lifestyle changes they have made will be reflected in their first weigh-in.




Operation Transformation - Series 7, Episode 4

Kathryn Thomas catches up with the next three leaders to see how they have adjusted to their first week of the plan, and looks at obesity and blood pressure.




Original Air Dates: 14-Jan-2014 and 15-Jan-2014
